    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras/22233959bf33109338adcabe2ee40e32.avif?t=1730375580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras_big/22233959bf33109338adcabe2ee40e32.avif?t=1730375580 width=800 height=554 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Suho Defense</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suho Defense is a top-view style multiplay defense game. Experience battles and cool characters, and win the game with strategic judgment and flashy battle play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras/f9496d9bbd0e8ae93d5c64b0971172bd.avif?t=1730375580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras_big/f9496d9bbd0e8ae93d5c64b0971172bd.avif?t=1730375580 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade, Cooperate! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use achievements and cooperative bosses to get rewards and upgrade your character. Defeat the enemies and bosses that keep coming to win the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras/9dbfe6b46073cb4b2018c75c03e368e5.avif?t=1730375580\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236600/extras_big/9dbfe6b46073cb4b2018c75c03e368e5.avif?t=1730375580 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy various characters in your own style.</p>",
